Package irgroupproject.qp.token

Class Summary
Operator Simple POJO used to represent one our allowed query operators {AND, OR, NEAR, NOT}.
Term Term object, representing a word in a user query.
Token Generic Token definition.

Tokens can be either a term (world, baseball, etc) or a operator (and, or, near).
TokenList Simple list used to keep track of our located tokens in the user supplied query.
 

Enum Summary
OperatorType Utility class providing some static methods used to distinguish operator type tokens stored as strings.
 

Exception Summary
InvalidTokenRelationshipException Simple token related exception that extends QueryParserException
